## How to Use This Milestone

### For Developers
1. Clone the workspace
2. Follow [QUICKSTART.md](../../../core/vi/docs/00-overview/QUICKSTART.md)
3. Server runs on localhost:3001
4. CLI available via `npm run cli`

### For Testing
```bash
cd core/vi
npm install
npm run type-check
npm run build
npm start  # Terminal 1
# In Terminal 2:
npm run cli -- --version
npm run cli -- interactive
```

